      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal mapping between validation experiment input parameters and COU input parameters with documented equivalency justification.",
      "rationale": "No formal equivalency mapping was produced between the FDA pump test conditions and the target VAD COU; differences in fluid temperature, hematocrit, and inlet waveform shape were noted but not formally addressed."
